    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon leather. At the heart of this machine is the S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system that pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory variable M-differential. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup for exceptional lateral grip. While the exterior shows minor road-rash consistent with spirited use, the chassis remains rigid and the engine's compression is within factory specifications. This is an mechanically sound, analog performance icon ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
